All the creatures in that place would have hightened sense of hearing or smell. Like the bats as they go out in dark and use ecolocation.  These alien wont live long in a planet full of light as the inhabitants of that planet would have developed eyes and hence they can locate them easily and make them a target much easily.  They practically should have beacome extinct by now.  People in the movie are just lazy and busy hiding all the time. They need to get out and take the planet back from them.
